item.title: My RuneScape Account... Tell me what you think
item.dc:creator: @Coca_Cola Coca Cola
item.description:
@Coca_Cola wrote:

Don’t boast when you arn’t that great.

The average combat in RS2 is 97 or so, so you’re not high up that way. Your woodcutting is ok, but 57 magic = BAD, I don’t know why you highlighted, and I get 750K an hour.

Sorry, I’m not saying you’re shit or anything, but you say you’re great, and you’re not. Better than a lot of mopar-ers though.

~Cola
